# Nordic Electricity Market Intelligence & Price Forecasting Platform

An AI-driven electricity market analytics and forecasting platform built using real Finland day-ahead electricity pricing data from the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform. This project focuses on electricity market trend analysis, price forecasting, volatility detection, and energy market intelligence using machine learning and time-series analytics.

---

## Project Overview

This project was developed to analyze real-world electricity market behavior in the Nordic energy sector using Finland’s electricity market pricing data. The platform performs data preprocessing, exploratory data analysis, machine learning-based forecasting, and market volatility analysis to generate actionable energy market insights.

The system demonstrates how AI and data analytics can support electricity market forecasting and smart energy decision-making.

---

## Features

* Real Finland electricity market data analysis
* Day-ahead electricity price forecasting
* Time-series analytics and trend analysis
* Electricity market volatility detection
* Hourly, daily, and monthly price pattern analysis
* Feature engineering for energy market forecasting
* Machine learning model training and evaluation
* Interactive data visualizations
* Forecasting performance analysis

