---

## Dataset Information

The dataset was collected from the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform and contains real Finland electricity market pricing data.

### Dataset Includes:

* Timestamp
* Day-ahead electricity prices (EUR/MWh)
* High-frequency market intervals
* Historical electricity pricing trends

---

## Project Workflow

### 1. Data Collection

Real Finland electricity market data was downloaded from the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform.

### 2. Data Cleaning & Preprocessing

* Removed unwanted columns
* Handled missing values
* Converted timestamps
* Processed electricity pricing data

### 3. Feature Engineering

Created:

* Hour
* Day
* Month
* Weekday
* Year-based features

### 4. Exploratory Data Analysis

Performed:

* Electricity price trend analysis
* Hourly price analysis
* Monthly trend analysis
* Weekday pricing analysis

### 5. Machine Learning Forecasting

Trained a Random Forest Regression model to predict electricity prices based on time-related features.

### 6. Model Evaluation

Evaluated forecasting performance using:

* MAE
* MSE
* RMSE
* R² Score

### 7. Volatility Detection

Detected abnormal electricity price fluctuations and market instability patterns.

---

## Machine Learning Model

### Model Used

* Random Forest Regressor

### Input Features

* Hour
* Day
* Month
* Weekday

### Target Variable

* Electricity Price (EUR/MWh)

